Package it.polimi.ingsw.common.models

Class AmmoCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.common.models.AmmoCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Displayable, java.io.Serializable 
    public class AmmoCard
extends java.lang.Object
implements Displayable, java.io.Serializable
    This class contains all the information about an ammo card. Each card is composed of three elements, one on top, and two on bottom, one left and one right. The top element can be an ammo ( with color ) or a power up. The two bottom elements are ammo, they can be of the same or different ( just in case of power up on top ) color.
